nattupura pattu is a 1996 tamil language drama film directed by kasthuri raja .   the film features selva , sivakumar and kushboo in lead roles , with manorama , goundamani , senthil , vinu chakravarthy , kumarimuthu , prem , anusha and abhirami playing supporting roles .   the film , produced by vijayalakshmi kasthuri raja , had musical score by ilaiyaraaja and was released on 9 february 1996 .